description: Extension to time limit of application 05/0380 dated 12/05/05 for demolition of existing building and replacement with a 5- and part 6-storey building to provide a mixed-use development including basement car-parking, retail at ground and mezzanine levels, and 73 flats in 2 separate blocks and subject to a Deed of Agreement dated 12th August 2010 under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990, as amended.  This represents a car-free development
